edu.ucla.sspace.dependency

Interface DependencyPermutationFunction<T extends Vector>

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    DefaultDependencyPermutationFunction, RelationPermutationFunction, RelationSumPermutationFunction

    public interface DependencyPermutationFunction<T extends Vector>
    An interface for permuting a Vector based on a dependecny path, represented as a list of DependencyRelations. Implemenations are recomended to extend existing PermutationFunctions but simply using an existing PermutationFunction. Implementations are also suggested to be thread-safe.
    Author:
    Keith Stevens
    See Also:
    PermutationFunction
